item.description:
@MistaBigBoss wrote:

[quote=“rip4d, post:57, topic:520221”]It bugs me how the only remotely recent posts you’ve made here were basically just advertising this project/community of yours.[/quote]Yeah I know, I’ve been too busy lately to be active on moparscape lately. But I got bored and remembered the time I used to spend on the model section, so I thought why not make a visit. That is when I came across this topic with these awesome models, and I need someone like the OP for my project, so I made a reply here. The post I made here was only meant for poopler, it was not meant as advertisement. I didn’t know how his PM box was doing so I had to post here (with info about the project) to be sure he got the message. The other posts you’re referring to were made in a topic I created at the launch of the project in the “Talk about other games” board to attract some people. I don’t see how any of this could possibly bug some random guy.

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:56, topic:520221”]I don’t like how your intro is like 30 seconds of “bla bla bla I made this”
Also, the sprinting is nasty…[/quote]That’s too bad. It would be superficial to just show random game-play without any explanation of what it’s about, that is why an intro (especially for the first video of a project) is necessary.

I know the sprinting isn’t what it should be, but animating a placeholder character isn’t a priority right now.
